\": 348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"score\": 0.5831405063198644, \"rank\": 0.7148248930372914, \"text\": \"Alexandria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 300}, {\"ngram\": \"quite a few titles\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest man\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"the world and Olympic gold medalist\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the most exciting day in the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most exciting day\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"said Lyles' uncle Rahsaan Caine.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.8012451082545924, \"rank\": 0.2389324733376107, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean, like, it's - it's priceless.\\\"\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Caine told WTOP that Lyles' skills were clear from a young age.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 560, \"end\": 565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.8012451082545924, \"rank\": 0.2389324733376107, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caine\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"WTOP\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I realized he was fast when he could beat me running,\\\" Caine said.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caine\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When he was about 13 years old - and I have always been really fast.\\\"\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 742, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And now, with Lyles already in the history books, Caine said it means even more to see all the people gathered from Alexandria to watch his nephew cross the finish line.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.8012451082545924, \"rank\": 0.2389324733376107, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aubrey_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 860, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"score\": 0.5831405063198644, \"rank\": 0.7148248930372914, \"text\": \"Alexandria\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the history books\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"Caine\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"his nephew\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Winning the gold is winning the gold for everybody.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's how I actually view it,\\\" he told WTOP.\", \"f